{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "云铮与艾天蝠在铁匠村外立圈比武，二人互让三招，云铮凭一股锐气与艾天蝠缠斗。艾天蝠被迫动用双掌，将云铮击伤倒地，但云铮顽强爬起，在极度缓慢的一掌中意外击中艾天蝠面颊。艾天蝠受辱欲自尽，跛足童子拼命阻拦。铁中棠暗中以冷言激怒艾天蝠，令其放弃求死转而追敌而去。温黛黛抱着重伤的云铮逃离，途中云铮误认柳荷衣为寒枫堡敌人，温黛黛只好带他冒雨奔回山中藏身之处。抵达时发现两名丫鬟已被沈杏白杀害。沈杏白与温黛黛互相试探算计，温黛黛施展美人计引诱，铁中棠突入窗中放走沈杏白作为金蝉脱壳之计，但艾天蝠识破骗局追至屋外。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "就在这里动手么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "这圈子不嫌太大了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "不论圈子大小，你我今日不分胜负，谁也不得出圈半步。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "让你三招，快动手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "云某焉肯先向盲瞎之人出手？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "糟了糟了，此番我也救不得他了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "在我大哥面前骂他瞎子的人，从来没有一个人能活在世上。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日若有谁人此圈子一步，助我云铮一拳半足，云某便立刻死在他面前。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "很好，不死不休。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们男人为什么这样奇怪，也没有什么深仇大恨，为什么要不死不休？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大哥，打他两拳就好了，何苦伤他的性命？他……他也没欺负我……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "你若再多口，我便先割下你的舌头。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少女",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "大爹可是要我去帮那少年么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "不错，快去救他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽不愿与男子动手，但大爹的话，我只有听从。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你若帮他，他便要横刀自刎，他的脾气我最清楚，说出的话，永远不会更改的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "小鬼，你难道真没有法子么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "惟一的办法，就是要姓云的莫要先动手，我大哥也从来不先向别人出手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "你不说这话，他也不会先动手的，但你这么样一说，他一定要先动手的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么知道他是这样的脾气？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我大哥说出的话，也是永远都不会更改的，他说让三招，就是让三招。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "再让你三招。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "偏不要你让！再回让你三招！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "再接我这三招！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的臭脾气，我倒真的从未见过。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "今日你总算见到了吧？小孩子长些见识也好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个倔强的少年！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到大旗门竟有这样的汉子，看来竟比老夫的脾气还要刚强几分。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我大哥已有多年未曾动用过双掌，此番竟被他逼得使了出来，他纵然输了，也光荣得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "输了就是输了，有什么光荣？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "下面三招，你还打得出手么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "好个老匹夫，先和俺打一场再说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你敢来助我一拳，我便先撞死在你面前。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "但他这三招，你是万万躲不过的，",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你怎知我躲不过……纵然躲不过，也与你无关。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "姓艾的，来吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "看你是条汉子，让你多喘息片刻。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "云大弟，你不能死的，你还有十五万两银子在我这里，你……你……你还年轻，正可享受一切，你就让别人帮帮你好么？我……我此后一定好好地待你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "难道……难道你不喜欢我了？我是喜欢你的呀！你若死了，要我……要我怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "我已喘过气来，你还不动手？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你方才说的盲瞎两字，可是骂的我么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "不是你不是你，他骂的不是你。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "你本是盲瞎之人，说的自然是你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "此刻你可愿收回？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "我又未曾说错，你本就是个瞎子。大丈夫一言既出，死也不会收回。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "好……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你……你为什么这样傻，你若……若说收回，他就不会伤你了呀！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大丈夫生若无愧，死有何惧？今日能见到你的眼泪，我已高兴得很。姓艾的，动手吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你还要再战？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大旗门下，从无中途告饶的人。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "姓艾的，我……我终于击中你一掌……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "艾天蝠，你还有脸向他出手么？有种的和俺海大少战一阵。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "这样的少年，是否已值得你出手了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "柳荷衣",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "艾天蝠，你可敢接我柳荷衣几招？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "老夫虽然是大旗门的仇人，今日也要与你拼上一场。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "你过来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大哥，你……你若不愿和他们动手，小弟可代你应战。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "不用说，站到我面前来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大哥，你……你这是做什么？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "我这一拜，是要你代我去拜师傅，对她老人家说，弟子艾天蝠，已再不能报她老人家的传艺之恩了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大哥，你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "艾天蝠纵横一生，今日被人手掌打在面上，还有脸再苟存人世么？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "但……但大哥你是先击伤他的呀！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "我意已决，你不必说了，代我问候众家弟妹，就说大哥已告别了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "云某既能置生死于度外，艾天蝠何又不能？九弟，你切莫忘记，男子汉死时要像个英雄。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛足童子",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "大哥，你不能死的……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "这样死了，也不算英雄。有种的就活下去，还不知有多少人要向你挑战呢！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_bo_zu_tong_zi",
      "text": "九弟，放手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人影",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "你们何必劝他，他这个瞎子，活在世上本无味，不如让他死了算了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "什么人敢辱骂于我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人影",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "骂了你又怎样？哈哈，你不过是个快要死的瞎子而已。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你过来，我纵然要死，也要等杀了你再死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人影",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "若是杀不了我又如何？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "艾天蝠",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "一日杀不了你，艾某便一日不死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人影",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "你杀不了我的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人不知是谁，倒的确高明得很，三言两语，便将艾天蝠一条命要回来了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "可要追去看看么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "追不上了，追不上了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "武振雄",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "姑娘不如留在此间……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "柳荷衣",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "待我先看看他的伤势。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "是她……是她……她是寒枫堡的人，黛黛……快……快走……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好……好，寒枫堡，我和你拼了……拼了！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "好，我们走，我们走……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "这……这……荷儿，去追……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "柳荷衣",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "大爹放心，他死不了的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莺儿、燕儿你们还未睡么？快准备些热水来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你怎会来了，还不声不响地杀了我丫鬟。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小侄怎敢伤害婶娘的丫鬟？小侄来时，还在奇怪她们怎会死了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "看你一身狼狈样子，婶娘我找件衣服给你换好么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "弟子奉家师之命前来问候婶娘，怎敢劳动婶娘？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你师傅叫你来问候我？他自己为何不来？难道是怕司徒笑吃醋么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "家师要小侄先来看看婶娘这里可方便，只怕他老人家也要来的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "看看这里可方便？哎哟，这里自然是方便的，你回去叫他来吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "但婶娘这里却不太方便，小侄怎敢如此回复师傅？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "有什么不方便？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "这位大旗门的高足，小侄也认得的，小侄见到，怎敢不说？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "哎哟，你是说他呀？你回去告诉黑星天，就说这人我已玩腻了，正想交给他们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你师傅平日就总是目不转睛地瞧着我，这次他找你来探路，还是为了……为了那事么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "像婶娘这样的美人，无论是哪个男子见了，都忍不住要动心的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "你呢？你想不想？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "speaker_name": "沈杏白",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小侄也是男人，怎会不想，只是不敢去想而已。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "现在，你还不敢么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "来吧，还等什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_shen_xing_bai",
      "text": "滚！若被我再追上你时，便没命了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_ai_tian_fu",
      "text": "你骗不了我的，逃出那人的身法，与你完全不同。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 613
    }
  ],
